raw_text = "~ start
Erika: Hello lovely pink bunny
PlayerM: Hello?
PlayerM: Is this the Sorority club?
Erika: Why yes, yes it is lovely
Erika: You must be Nina's darling girl, Mabel
PlayerM: Hi!
Nina: Tsk
Jessica: Hello Mabel, welcome to the Sorority!
Jessica: This is your initiation group chat
Jessica: The three of us will keep an eye out for you, making sure you fall in line with the rest of us
PlayerM: Hiya! Nice to meet you Jessica 😁
Jessica: Erika is right, what a darling you are
Jessica: I'm sure it'll be fun to... work with you
PlayerM: 😁
Jessica: Tell me Mabel, do you have any pics of pictures of yourself?
PlayerM: Yeah, I have a bunch on Social Scene
Mabel: img: mabel/98
PlayerM: Like this?
Erika: Oh my, what fun this will be
Jessica: Not quite
Jessica: I've seen those and I was thinking a little more brave
PlayerM: Brave? Like what?
Jessica: Like a bikini shot, or maybe a lingerie shot?
Jessica: Something we could hang up as a portrait
Jessica: Show everyone who Mabel really is
PlayerM: 😳
PlayerM: I already uhm... is that a requirement?
Jessica: Yes, it is
Jessica: When I ask something of you, it usually is a requirement
Jessica: I wouldn't waste your precious time
PlayerM: I see, okay!
PlayerM: And who's going to see the picture?
Jessica: We'll hang it up on the wall of girls in the lobby
Jessica: So everyone can see how hot you are
PlayerM: O-oh!! 🙃
PlayerM: I have to ask my boyfriend if that's okay
Nina: Tsk
Jessica: Part of the sorority rules dictates that you are a sorority member first
Jessica: While you're allowed to have that outside life, we don't really consider it here
PlayerM: What's that mean?
Erika: I have a boyfriend too honey but we still have to follow club rules 😘
Erika: Don't worry too much, you won't be forced to do anything you don't want to do
PlayerM: Okay, I guess that's just how clubs work huh
Jessica: Would you be able to take one by Monday?
PlayerM: I can try 😅
Jessica: Wonderful
Erika: Don't worry sweetheart, I know it's intimidating at first but you'll see a whole new side to you
Erika: img: nina/16
Erika: Something like this hun!
Nina: What the??
PlayerM: Wow, is that Nina?
PlayerM: Wow!! Pretty
Nina: Where the fuck did you get that??
Erika: Trade secret 🤭
Nina: You little bitch
Jessica: Girls, be nice or you'll do a shift at Queen's
Nina: Fuck that..
PlayerM: Shift at where? 😅
Jessica: You don't have to worry about that
Jessica: Just focus on your task sweetheart 😘
PlayerM: Oh so you want me to take a picture like that?
PlayerM: I guess I can try, it doesn't look so bad
PlayerM: I don't know if I have any clothes like that though
Jessica: If you do need, you can pick up the set we provide
Jessica: We'll go through it all in more detail on Monday when you come by the Sorority house
Jessica: By the way, do you plan to move in?
PlayerM: Oh I didn't know I could!
Erika: You should, the beds are much bigger and more comfortable than those tiny dorm room 🥰
Erika: Silk sheets and a bed big enough for a whole group 😉
Erika: And the girl gossip is soooo juicy honey
Nina: Not to mention only hot girls and hot guys, nothing less 😒
PlayerM: Maybe not then but I'll think about it 😅
Jessica: Lovely, if you change your mind, we can open up a room for you
Jessica: See you on Monday
PlayerM: Thanks, bye!
=> END"
